  <scopecontent id="aspace_0bbe8e9b4c0306c839c4bc291c8af0b6">
    <head>Content Description</head>
<p>Original artwork, lyrics manuscripts, a photograph, 2 news clippings, contracts and agreements, and ephemera by or pertaining to Joeski Love.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <bioghist id="aspace_ad35f6f18f3612d6d6720786455def6e">
    <head>Biographical / Historical</head>
<p>Joeski Love is a US Hip Hop artist from the Bronx best known for his platinum 1986 single "Pee Wee's Dance", which has been sampled numerous times. Love was originally part of a group signed by Vince Davis on his Elektra-owned Vintertainment imprint.</p>  </bioghist>
